room_title: Escape room "The Copper County Conviction" by Escape the cLock in Garden City
room_address: 124 N Main St Garden City, KS 67846
room_description: You thought this was going to be just another cattle drive when you left Boot Hill last week.  But the scandalous Copper County Sheriff had other plans for you!  He’s done gone and locked up one of your partners for no good reason!   You bust into the jail house to break ‘em out, when you discover there’s something far more nefarious going on…
